                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>This affliction can't be reduced below stage 1, nor the damage from it healed, until successfully treated with <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Remove Curse]</em> or a similar effect; the affliction can then be removed as a normal disease. A creature that dies from cold damage while cursed with blackfrost rises as a blackfrost dead after 24 hours. Blackfrost has a counteract level of 10.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:27]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r 4d6[cold]]] (1 minute)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> weakness to cold 5 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> weakness to cold 10 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} (1 day)</p>"
